data.description:
This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem awaits you! If you're seeking the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and serenity, this property has it all.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that immediately makes you feel right at home. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an airy and welcoming ambiance. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space for all your culinary adventures. Whether you're cooking up a feast for family and friends or enjoying a quiet meal, this kitchen is a true delight. The 3 bedrooms provide cozy retreats for everyone in the family. The primary suite boasts its own ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet, offering privacy and convenience. With ceiling fans throughout the home, you'll stay comfortable year-round.

One of the standout features of this property is the backyard. Imagine spending your evenings under the starlit Tucson skies, with no neighbors behind to disrupt your tranquility. This backyard is a blank canvas! Your next chapter starts here!
